## Acknowledgments

This project is a fork of
[coleam00/claude-memory-compiler](https://github.com/coleam00/claude-memory-compiler)
by Cole Medin, which is itself adapted from
[Andrej Karpathy's LLM Knowledge Base](https://gist.github.com/karpathy/442a6bf555914893e9891c11519de94f)
architecture.

At the time of forking (April 2026), the upstream repository did not include a
license file. A request to add one has been filed
(https://github.com/coleam00/claude-memory-compiler/issues/11). If the upstream
author chooses a license that imposes additional conditions, this project will
comply accordingly.
